{
  "chapter": 14,
  "chapter_summary": "第十四章讲述了萧秋水、唐方、左丘超然、邓玉函一行四人抵达贵州甲秀楼，却遭权力帮设伏。南宫松篁假扮伙计下毒，四人中毒后被柳有孔（不见天日）和钟无离（咽喉穿洞）制服。危急时刻，铁星月和邱南顾赶到，与钟无离、柳有孔展开激战。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我饿了。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难怪我们的遭遇，不会被录在传记里了。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不，你们一定会被记下来，",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们少年时就敢惹权力帮，冲出剑庐求援，对三才剑客饶而不杀，身上连一个钱也没有，还上甲秀楼大吃……",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们这些虽然不像故事中的大侠、侠女，但是你们更亲切、更真实、更人间………大家都怔让了。邓王函忍不住道：“",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好。从今以后，我们都不叫唐姑娘了，要直呼你唐方罗！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是。可是他们向不失约，而今未至，很可能是遭了权力帮的……",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不。我在放走劫生前有一条件，就是问明老铁和小邱的下落。据说是他们三次想自外攻人，但皆被挡了下来，之后生死不明了……",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可惜小邱也是疯疯癫癫的。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唐姑娘真是心细如发，三才剑客既截击我于桂湖，这一路上去桂林，绝不可能平静无波的，真的还是小心点儿好。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "百毒神魔的嫡传弟子与一洞神魔座下的西个宝贝，只怕也会跟上来。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些人还不怎样，要是康出渔、沙千灯等来了。倒是不易应付。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不过要是他们追来了，也等于是替浣花派引开了部分强敌。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我现在才真正感受到‘笑饮一杯酒，杀人都市中’的滋味。以前以为这是豪迈行止，后来想及被杀者的心情，却又是另一般滋味，死者的悲落却造成了杀人者的意气风发。唉！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "邓玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不过南宫松篁这种人，确实该死。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快快吃吧，吃饱了好赶路，早日到桂林，早日好。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们虽杀得了南宫松篁，却不料他一拍间下了毒，他料不到我们见死不救，却造成我们的得手，因你们中毒！哈哈哈哈……",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "而且这种毒啊，药力只盏茶的时间，就消失了，但我们呢？哪——",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哑穴",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "渊液穴",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "京门穴",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大椎穴",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "眼看你们功力恢复，但又被我们点了穴道，还是不能动、不能打、不能叫、不能生、不能死，哈哈哈哈……",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "而我们要你们怎样，你们就得怎样，哈哈哈……",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_you_kong",
      "speaker_name": "柳有孔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！你这臭小子敢看我不顺眼，我就要挖你双眼！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然知道叫什么楼了！大大个‘甲秀楼’写在上面，三里以外也看见啦！叫做甲秀楼！，’那粗声大汉怒道：“",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那边有条狗，我是说给狗听！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放屁！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "狗放屁！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你屁放狗！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他妈的！笑什么笑！笑你没有嘴巴啊？！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "尖声大汉径自在笑，粗声大汉忽然怒喝一声，呼地打出一·拳，尖声大汉声音陡止，也呼地打出一拳人听“",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你没有理由笑，我笑就可以！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说的？！屁明明可以放狗，不信，我放给你看！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "屁哪里可以看的！又不是脱裤子放屁！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那你不着，可以听啊，请君为我倾耳听，听好了蔼—？",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁是屁王？",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好吧……",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喀，这楼原来是饭馆，怎么招牌是空白的？",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "空白招牌，不行，让我上去摘下来看看……",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "……力……什么……欢……又不是欢……什么力……什么居……",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "岂有此理，谁叫他的楷书写得那么乱，不会写字！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放屁！是草书！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯？怎么有楼没有人？有菜没伙计的？’邱南顾却喜道：“",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是饿扁了，总之有好吃的，全部拿来！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是是是。",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喂，掌柜的，旁边是你的伙计吗？",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是不是，这是我弟弟……",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "赫！怎么他这么凶神恶煞！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唉呀客官有所不知，我弟弟他是个白痴……",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "白痴？",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "打成白痴？好高的武功！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一口猪！哪里会把一个人打成一口猪！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真他妈的老子又没惹你，你干吗骂人是猪！",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "打他的人是谁？",
      "tone": "normal",
      "chapter": 14
    }
  ],
